<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.5">
<l>maṭi vaḻivantu nīrpulaṉ cōra</l>
<l rend="indent">vāyi laṭṭiya kañciyum mīṇṭē</l>
<l>kaṭai vaḻivārak kaṇṭama ṭaippak</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṇṇu ṟakkama tāvataṉ muṉṉam</l>
<l>tuṭai vaḻiyummai nāykaḷ kavarā</l>
<l rend="indent">cūlat tālummaip pāyvatuñ ceyyār</l>
<l>iṭai vaḻiyilnīr kūṟaiyumi ḻavīr</l>
<l rend="indent">iruṭī kēcaṉeṉ ṟēttaval līrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As piss trickles through [your] clothes,</l>
<l rend="indent">[your] throat closes so that conjee</l>
<l rend="indent">poured in [your] mouth, passing through,</l>
<l rend="indent">dribbles from [your] lips,</l>
<l rend="indent">and [your] eyes sleep [forever] –</l>
<l>before that happens,</l>
<l>you are able to praises Hṛṣīkeśa</l>
<l rend="indent">so that dogs do not bite at your thighs,</l>
<l>they don’t leap at you with tridents,</l>
<l rend="indent">and you don’t lose the clothes at [your] waist.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
